Package burlap.behavior.singleagent.vfa.rbf

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DistanceMetric
    An interface for defining distant metrics between OO-MDP State objects.
    FVDistanceMetric
    An interface for defining the distance between two states that are represented with double arrays.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FVRBF
    A class for defining radial basis functions for states represented with a double array.
    FVRBFFeatureDatabase
    A feature database of RBF units that can be used for linear value function approximation.
    RBF
    An abstract class for defining RBF units.
    RBFFeatureDatabase
    A feature database of RBF units that can be used for linear value function approximation.
